text: Came to witness my nephew graduating. Nice parade. Kudos to the team that arrange transportation pickup for elderly. It helps my elderly mom able to walk at minimum distance and enable her to walk to her sitting area quickly and for her to see her grandson graduated today.
Was there for the Change of Command of our Chief Defence Force.
Singapore's most well known military institute.
My friend graduated from here. Now he has a girlfriend and he leads excels and overcomes.
Let's hope I get a chance to complete OCS
